Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.49,0:00:12.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\pos(324,180)\fnArial\b1\fs12\shad0\3c&HB4CBA1&\c&H424A29&\blur2}Hozuki Ichi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:15.29,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,The special theatrical showcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.13,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,I guess it is that time already.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.76,0:00:20.25,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We're definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:22.99,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,getting our revenge this year.
