Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.77,0:09:21.28,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wh-What's wrong, you three?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.03,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,She's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.80,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Not you too, Sasuga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.29,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnImpact\shad0\bord3\c&HEA3B53&\fs36\an8}Menacing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.29,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Wait, everyone's doing it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.28,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Who are you all talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.20,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Chika Nanase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.56,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,A grade school girl who goes\Nto about 400 plays a year,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.92,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,earning her the nickname\N"the Theater Professor."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:47.29,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,She's why the boss really \Nwanted to do {\i1}King Lear{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.55,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.15,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,After last year's show...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:55.98,Flashback,Chika,0,0,0,,I truly felt SIRIUS's soul in making\Na brave choice like {\i1}King Lear{\i0} so boldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:59.92,Flashback,Chika,0,0,0,,But did you forget that your audience \Ntoday was grade school students?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:03.21,Flashback,Chika,0,0,0,,With that in mind, you should have chosen\Nsomething to make SIRIUS shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:07.75,Flashback,Chika,0,0,0,,As someone who's followed SIRIUS for years,\NI was disappointed with this {\i1}King Lear{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.08,Flashback,Chika,0,0,0,,To quickly sum up everything wrong \Nwith this performance in an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:15.07,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,She gave notes to Hiiragi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.07,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What a terrifying grade schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.41,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,She told us off, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:20.50,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:22.27,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,So, Koko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:26.90,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,We absolutely {\i1}cannot{\i0} lose this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:28.52,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,"Battle"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.52,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Sassu! This time, we'll \Nreally knock her socks off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:35.90,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I'd love to make her \Nput a sock in it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.03,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,We'll sock it to her, for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:42.40,Main,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,We'll start rehearsal in ten.\NMake sure you're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.41,Main,All,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:46.11,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Things seem to be taking shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.16,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,They're so motivated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.27,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
