Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:01.15,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,I know that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:03.58,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,Art thou not Romeo and a Montague?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:07.58,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Neither, fair maid, if either thee dislike.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:09.36,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,And but thou love me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.36,0:11:13.08,Main,Kokona,0,0,0,,This is just the first rehearsal, \Nbut they're so in sync.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:14.61,Main,Kathrina,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.66,Main,Shizuka,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:22.20,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,I suddenly want to be up on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.47,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,My life were better ended by\Ntheir hate than death proroguèd,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:28.38,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,wanting of thy love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:33.40,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,She's always so spacey, but she \Ncompletely changes onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:39.47,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,I used to be so jealous of Sassu,\N who could do everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:48.07,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,Sassu and I were childhood friends \Nwho lived near each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:50.01,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,We were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.78,0:11:56.39,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,That cloud looks yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.79,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,School's this way, dang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:58.79,Flashback - Overlap,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.42,0:12:03.92,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,So I always had a front-row seat\Nto how impressive she was.
