Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.67,Flashback,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.50,Flashback,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.56,Flashback,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.69,Flashback,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Sasuga-chan, the swim team wanted you\Nas a backup swimmer, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.47,Flashback,Girl 2,0,0,0,,And you got scouted as a model?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.98,Flashback,Girl 3,0,0,0,,Is it true that you found some edible ants?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:47.01,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Starting today, we're rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:48.19,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Rivals?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.17,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,It means we're enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:52.42,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.00,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Everyone just keeps talking about Sassu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:03.10,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I'm special too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.73,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.96,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I'm not talking to you anymore, Sassu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.21,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.67,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Because we're rivals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:11.39,Flashback,Young sasuga,0,0,0,,Oh...
