Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.87,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.87,0:13:19.49,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,{\i1}Romeo and Juliet{\i0}!
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.49,0:13:20.75,Main,Girls,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.16,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:24.24,Flashback,Girl 1,0,0,0,,There's a special theatrical showcase!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:25.87,Flashback,Girl 2,0,0,0,,And SIRIUS is doing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.77,Flashback,Girl 3,0,0,0,,SIRIUS is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.52,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,SIRIUS...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:34.25,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs14\shad0\bord0\c&HAE9EB2&\frz5.11\pos(310,73.333)}Special Theatrical Showcase
