Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.06,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I won a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.81,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Once I get famous here, \NI'll finally be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.50,Flashback,Young sasuga,0,0,0,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.06,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Sassu?! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.67,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,I won a ticket too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.49,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.64,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Huh? H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.06,0:14:07.76,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.78,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:13.67,Flashback - Italics,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could be up on stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:17.81,Flashback - Italics,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could be just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.51,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I want to be on that stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:28.29,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,I want to be a Dai Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:29.55,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.35,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.88,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,If you're gonna do it, I want to do it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:37.42,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.70,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Why do you keep getting in my way, Sassu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.81,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Art, the pull-up bars, even swimming!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.43,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,How come you can do it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:51.95,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,You can do everything better \Nthan me... so why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.21,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,I want to see the same world as you, Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.95,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:03.41,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,You've got a good head on your shoulders \Nand you always think about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.20,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,That's why I like you, Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.21,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.47,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.47,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Say more of my good traits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.74,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.98,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.79,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,And... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.35,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Oh, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:30.70,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,You should've said that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:40.05,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, fine. I guess you're \Njust useless without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:47.38,Flashback,Young Panda,0,0,0,,Let's do this, then! You'll become a Dai Star\Nwith me, the world's cutest Panda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:49.85,Flashback,Young Sasuga,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.20,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:16:01.34,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. I was just reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:06.15,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\shad0\frz331.6\c&H08193A&\3c&H345588&\b1\frx18\fry26\pos(221.334,118.667)}Monja Asakusa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:13.05,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,It's been some time, Miss Niizuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.07,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Hello, Nanase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:17.45,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0} was fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:21.71,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,Your performance was on par with the \Nactors of SIRIUS's golden age.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.08,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:26.75,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,I wasn't very interested in this \Nproduction because you're not in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.85,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,but I figured I could kill\N some time since I won a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.34,0:16:34.10,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,I hope this won't damage the renown\Nyou earned with {\i1}Arabian Nights{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:38.62,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. SIRIUS only delivers the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:39.32,Main,Chika,0,0,0,,Oho?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:43.09,Main,Niizuma,0,0,0,,They might even sock it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.61,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,Let's bring the house down, Sassu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.14,Main - Italics,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Let's go, Panda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.96,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Two households, both alike in dignity,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.62,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,in fair Verona, where we lay our scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:09.87,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,The Capulets and the Montagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:14.15,Main,Kokona (Benvolio),0,0,0,,From ancient grudge break to new mutiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:18.27,Main,Kathrina (Father Laurence),0,0,0,,where civil blood makes civil hands unclean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:22.02,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,From forth the fatal loins\Nof these two foes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.19,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,whose misadventured piteous overthrows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.78,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,doth with their death bury...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.28,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,their parents' strife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:43.53,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,They're following the original play\Nwhile adding a SIRIUS twist. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.18,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,O Juliet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:54.93,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Did my heart love till now? Forswear it, sight!\NFor I ne'er saw true beauty till this night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:18:00.52,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,O Romeo, if you love me, \Ntell me from your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.12,Main - Italics,Panda,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.89,0:18:16.94,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,And it was all going so well\Nup until now. How disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:32.20,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Let us swear under the holy moon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.83,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,the love from our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.47,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,What?! That was part of the act?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.72,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,I've never seen such a beautiful \Nproposal from Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:45.76,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Chisa's Sense allows her to incorporate\Nany mistake made onstage
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.24,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,into part of the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:53.74,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,Her carefree nature turns it into \Nan elegant form of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.25,Main - Italics,Girl A,0,0,0,,Romeo's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:58.05,Main - Italics,Girl B,0,0,0,,Juliet is so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:03.62,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,And Panda can control the stage\Nby reading the audience's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:08.04,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,When their two Senses \Nwork together perfectly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:12.56,Main - Italics,Hiiragi,0,0,0,,they take the crowd into\N the palm of their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:25.14,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Juliet! Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:37.23,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,My love, my wife... I won't leave you \Nall alone in this tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:56.18,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Thou detestable maw...\Ngrant me sweet death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:03.51,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Here's to my beloved Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:08.38,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:11.28,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Juliet? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:16.30,Main,PAnda (Juliet),0,0,0,,The friar gave me medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:19.91,Main,PAnda (Juliet),0,0,0,,Medicine to make it appear\Nas if I were no longer alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:25.09,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,For if I were dead, I would be free\Nof my engagement to Count Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:28.73,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,We'd be free from our crimes.\NAnd I could live my life with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.43,0:20:33.75,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,Thank you, Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:40.67,Main,Sasuga (Romeo),0,0,0,,This love of ours should be able to end\Nthe feud between our families.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.77,Main,Panda (Juliet),0,0,0,,Yes, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.25,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.51,Main - Italics,Chika,0,0,0,,This is the soul of SIRIUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:10.09,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Hey, Sassu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:11.44,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.89,0:23:15.71,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,Do you think we measured up\Nto that other performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:19.67,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I dunno, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:21.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\b1\fnTimes New Roman\i1\shad0\c&HC9EFF4&\3c&H53647D&\4c&H535151&\pos(322,69.333)}Romeo & Juliet
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:21.96,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(252,166.667)\fnArial\fs12\shad0\frz9.354\c&HC0C3DE&\3c&H2F286C&}Chisa Sasuga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.34,Main,Sasuga,0,0,0,,I think this will make a great memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.30,0:23:28.11,Main,Panda,0,0,0,,I hope so.
